Package: klon
Architecture: all
Depends: ${python3:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}, python3-gi, gir1.2-gtk-4.0, gir1.2-adw-1, udisks2, coreutils, pkexec, python3-requests
Description: System cloning and recovery tool
 Klon is a simple utility to clone your entire OS drive for backup and recovery.
 It features a modern GTK4 interface and supports creating bootable recovery media.
